We use a centralized logger defined in the `@rccyx/logger` package. This ensures consistent, structured logging throughout the codebase for better maintainability.

---

## Logger Usage

Always import the logger from the package:

```ts
import { logger } from "@rccyx/logger";
```

NEVER EVER USE `console.log` or any other logger. There's only one.
